---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="公开课｜亚马逊 AI 运营实战课与资料领取" description="阿岩亚马逊 AI 运营公开课入口，面向想提升选品、Listing、广告 PPC 和 Review 分析效率的跨境电商卖家。">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <h1>阿岩亚马逊 AI 实战公开课</h1>
      <p>第一场公开课建议主题：AI 时代亚马逊卖家如何重做 Listing 和广告。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="topic-intro">
      <h2>公开课不是培训，是把方法论现场跑一遍</h2>
      <p>阿岩的公开课不讲虚的：不开场就讲工具、不承诺月入几万、不收 9980 的私董会。一场课两个小时，目标是把一个具体问题讲透：AI 怎么用、坑在哪、什么场景下不要用。</p>
      <p>每场公开课都有完整讲义、录播、Q&amp;A 整理，所有报名学员可同步领取最新一版 AI 运营资料包。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-2">
      <div class="card course-detail">
        <h3>近期课程</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">主题：<strong>AI 时代亚马逊卖家的机会与挑战</strong></p>
        <p class="course-meta">时间：6/12（周四）20:00 直播</p>
        <p class="course-meta">形式：腾讯会议直播 + 录播回看</p>
        <p class="course-meta">费用：免费预约</p>
        <a class="course-cta" href="/lead/">免费预约</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card course-detail">
        <h3>你将学到</h3>
        <ul class="course-points">
          <li>AI 工具在亚马逊运营中的真实定位</li>
          <li>用 AI 重做 Listing 标题、五点和 A+ 的流程</li>
          <li>AI 复盘广告报表的最小动作</li>
          <li>从 Review 里提炼卖点的 Prompt 模板</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="course-cta-secondary" href="/ai-amazon/">先看 AI 运营专题 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .topic-intro {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fbfdff 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.95);
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  }

  .topic-intro h2 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 12px;
  }

  .topic-intro h2::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 4px;
    width: 4px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #1368ff;
  }

  .topic-intro p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .topic-intro p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .course-detail .course-meta {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .course-points {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding-left: 22px;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .course-points li {
    margin: 6px 0;
  }

  .course-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 11px;
    background: #1368ff;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .course-cta-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
</style>
